            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": "The barbarian initially pelts enemies with arrows to deliver disabling critical hit effects, and dispatches any who survive with her flashing blade. In either case, she uses her speed to stay out of danger and her <i>boots of speed </i>to maximize movement or make full attacks in melee or at range."
            },
